rows.label: tlk41700122_06_msg0001
rows.name:
A lot of refugees from Acedia have
streamed into this city, but as long
as we have Kloom Farm, we'll be fine.

rows.label: tlk41700122_06_msg0002
rows.name:
Whether it's a hundred or a
thousand people, our vegetables
will see them fed.

rows.label: tlk41700122_06_msg0003
rows.name:
Every single vegetable from our farm
is packed so densely, there's no way
anyone could be left wanting more.

rows.label: tlk41700122_06_msg0004
rows.name:
Hahaha! This is the fruit of
our family's efforts, passed
down through the generations.
